OL,3,CMorrissey calls off concert after
OL,4,C'sleep deprivation' due to local
OL,5,Cfestival
OL,7,FMorrissey has called off a concert in
OL,8,FSpain after celebrations for a local
OL,9,Ffestival prevented him from getting a
OL,10,Fgood night's sleep.
OL,12,FThe "scheduled show in Valencia has
OL,13,Fbeen rendered impossible due to sleep
OL,14,Fdeprivation", a statement posted on
OL,15,Fthe website of the former The Smiths
OL,16,Ffrontman said.
OL,26,@tD@EOUvD@LO]
