OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773414686
OL,3,CMorrissey calls off concert after
OL,4,C'sleep deprivation' due to local
OL,5,Cfestival
OL,7,FMorrissey arrived in Valencia on
OL,8,FWednesday after a two-day drive from
OL,9,FMilan, but he was disturbed during the
OL,10,Fnight by a festival that included, the
OL,11,Fstatement said, "loud techno singing
OL,12,F(and) megaphone announcements" that
OL,13,Fwere audible from inside his hotel
OL,14,Froom.
OL,16,F"This experience has left Morrissey in
OL,17,Fa catatonic state," the statement read.
OL,26,@sD@QOUtD@^O]xD@AOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
