PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773414686
OL,3,CMorrissey calls off concert after
OL,4,C'sleep deprivation' due to local
OL,5,Cfestival
OL,7,FIt added in bold that: "The show is
OL,8,Fnot cancelled. Circumstances render
OL,9,Fthe show impossible", leaving it
OL,10,Funclear whether the concert will be
OL,11,Frescheduled or if ticket holders can
OL,12,Frequest a refund.
OL,14,FOn his website Morrissey said his
OL,15,Fhotel was "indescribable hell. It will
OL,16,Ftake me one year to recover. And that
OL,17,Fis an understatement".
OL,26,@oD@XOUqD@TO]
