OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773414686
OL,3,CMorrissey calls off concert after
OL,4,C'sleep deprivation' due to local
OL,5,Cfestival
OL,7,FThe 66-year-old Morrissey is touring
OL,8,Fto promote his album Make-up Is a Lie
OL,9,F- his first in six years - which was
OL,10,Freleased earlier this month. It is his
OL,11,Ffourteenth solo album.
OL,13,FWhile loved by his fans for timeless
OL,14,Fhits such as How Soon Is Now? and
OL,15,FEveryday Is Like Sunday, Morrissey is
OL,16,Falso known for his temperamental
OL,17,Fcharacter and wide array of shifting
OL,18,Fpolitical views.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
