OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773414686
OL,3,CMorrissey calls off concert after
OL,4,C'sleep deprivation' due to local
OL,5,Cfestival
OL,7,FHis support of animal rights has made
OL,8,Fhim a fierce critic of Spain's
OL,9,Ftraditional bullfights, for example.
OL,11,FThe Las Fallas festival in Valencia,
OL,12,Fon Spain's eastern Mediterranean
OL,13,Fcoast, is famous for its noisy street
OL,14,Fparties and fireworks.
OL,16,FIt culminates in the burning of huge,
OL,17,Fhandmade papier-mache sculptures.
OL,26,@yD@Urr
