OL,3,CMorrissey calls off concert after
OL,4,C'sleep deprivation' due to local
OL,5,Cfestival
OL,7,FUnesco added Las Fallas to its
OL,8,Fcatalogue of intangible cultural
OL,9,Fheritage in 2016 - it describes the
OL,10,Fincineration of the sculptures as "a
OL,11,Fform of purification" and "social
OL,12,Frenewal".
